OL,4,G2200FIbsen: The Wild Duck
OL,5,     GThe 1971 adaption of the classic
OL,6,     Gplay by Henrik Ibsen. A family's
OL,7,     Gfragile peace is shattered by an
OL,8,     Gidealist who insists on exposing
OL,9,     Ghidden truths.
OL,10,G2350FThe Australian Wars
OL,11,     GHow the growing number of
OL,12,     GEuropean arrivals in Tasmania saw
OL,13,     Gthe death count grow, too.
OL,14,G0050FThe Secret World of Haute Couture
OL,15,     GMargy Kinmonth meets millionaire
OL,16,     Gcustomers and world-famous
OL,17,     Gdesigners as she explores the
OL,18,     Ganachronistic but little-
OL,19,     Gexplained pocket of the fashion
OL,20,     Gindustry known as haute couture.
